{"tid":2151514,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"寫到最後一刻-馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-11T12:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T12:08:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1623c11411c52617c37b8c292cccd1cf19e893b4","tid":2151514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/AV7BME35K5GT7FTTGZ4I65KEWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FAV7BME35K5GT7FTTGZ4I65KEWU%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=6e7f51fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FAV7BME35K5GT7FTTGZ4I65KEWU%2F&h=37e8809c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/AV7BME35K5GT7FTTGZ4I65KEWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n寫到最後一刻-馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YNYm2GGNOds9FnmL_sAA88D12q4=/4865x3055/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MAO5RWMCYZDLDA3USJIVUWVFAI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYNYm2GGNOds9FnmL_sAA88D12q4%3D%2F4865x3055%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMAO5RWMCYZDLDA3USJIVUWVFAI.JPG&h=8de60d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二零二零年八月十日一覺醒來，就見證如夢如幻的歷史一刻：二百警察浩浩蕩蕩進入壹傳媒大樓，大肆搜查，多位高層包括黎智英被捕。縱然是早已預期的場面，但真正發生的時候仍然令人目瞪口呆。可預期跟可接受，畢竟是不同的。<br />\n<br />\n我不懂惺惺作態說什麼「一笑置之」，更不可能假裝一切正常。看。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記得一兩年前，編輯女士數次邀我到將軍澳看看，又盛讚公司飯堂的燒鵝。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n然而我也不是從未踏足壹傳媒大樓，只是僅僅到過大堂位置（就是這天我在新。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這樣強調那碟燒鵝，並非。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這個專欄可以寫到什麼日子，沒法預計。但從今以後，我寫的每一篇，都會當作是最後一篇，像西方古諺提倡的生活態度：「抱着明天就會死去的心情來活。」悲哀之餘，但願眾人不會喪失鬥志，因為「軟弱是可憐的，不管是行動抑或忍受。」（To be weak is miserable/ Doing or suffering）怕來不及道別，今天先草草寫下這些不成章的感想，共勉之。"}]}